Lee has won a myriad of major international awards, including 3 [[Academy Award]]s, 3 [[BAFTA Award]]s, 3 [[Golden Globe Award]]s; 3 [[Independent Spirit Award]]s ; 2 [[Golden Lion]] awards and 2 [[Golden Bear]] awards.

